OL,3,CWoman accused of slashing sister's
OL,4,Cthroat felt 'unappreciated', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA woman accused of cutting her film
OL,8,Fdirector sister's throat and stealing
OL,9,Fher Rolex felt "unappreciated" by her,
OL,10,Fa court heard.
OL,12,FNancy Pexton, 70, allegedly slashed
OL,13,Fand stabbed her sibling, Jennifer
OL,14,FAbbott, at her flat in Camden, north
OL,15,FLondon, on June 10 last year.
OL,17,FThree days later, a neighbour broke
OL,18,Fdown the door and found 69-year-old Ms
OL,19,FAbbott dead on the floor of her living
OL,20,Froom with gaffer tape covering her
OL,21,Fmouth.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@^O]
