CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776345056
OL,3,CWoman accused of slashing sister's
OL,4,Cthroat felt 'unappreciated', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAt the Old Bailey on Tuesday, Ms
OL,8,FAbbott's son Brad Carlson told jurors
OL,9,Fabout the "bubbling" resentment
OL,10,Fbetween his mother and aunt.
OL,12,FGiving evidence via video-link, Mr
OL,13,FCarlson said: "There was interaction
OL,14,Fand sometimes anger and hostility
OL,15,Fbetween my mother and Nancy, there was
OL,16,Fresentment seemingly bubbling up."
OL,18,FHe told the court he had received a
OL,19,Fnumber of messages from Pexton
OL,20,Fexpressing her "anger and resentment
OL,21,Fand furiousness" towards Ms Abbott.
OL,26,@qD@KOUqD@TO]uD@OOUxD@bO]|D@POU}D@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
