OL,3,CWoman accused of slashing sister's
OL,4,Cthroat felt 'unappreciated', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Carlson continued: "She was angry `
OL,8,FI think there was at times a feeling
OL,9,Fof disrespect.
OL,11,F"I think a feeling that she was
OL,12,Funappreciated and that my mother had
OL,13,Fnot shown gratitude for some of the
OL,14,Fthings Nancy had done and been there
OL,15,Ffor her."
OL,26,@oD@WOUsD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
