PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776345056
OL,3,CWoman accused of slashing sister's
OL,4,Cthroat felt 'unappreciated', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe victim's diamond-encrusted gold
OL,8,FRolex watch was missing when she was
OL,9,Ffound and was later recovered from
OL,10,FPexton's belongings after she was
OL,11,Fadmitted to hospital, jurors have
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FMr Carlson, who bought his mother the
OL,15,FRolex, said he "wanted people to get
OL,16,Falong" and encouraged them to make
OL,17,F"peace".
OL,26,@wD@POUxD@FO]yD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
