CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776345056
OL,3,CWoman accused of slashing sister's
OL,4,Cthroat felt 'unappreciated', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"I, at times, was very honest with my
OL,8,Fmother. I asked my mother to be more
OL,9,Fgentle and sometimes more careful in
OL,10,Fher words. Sometimes people need to be
OL,11,Ftreated more gently," said Mr Carlson.
OL,13,FHe added that he felt "empathy" and
OL,14,F"love" for Nancy.
OL,16,FThe court also heard that Ms Abbott
OL,17,Fhad told her nephew Feras Abukhait she
OL,18,Fthought Pexton was "capable of
OL,19,Fanything", and that she feared for her
OL,20,Fsafety.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@UO]uD@WOUuD@_O]vD@AOUvD@FO]zD@
OL,26,ATOU{D@IO]
