OL,3,CWoman accused of slashing sister's
OL,4,Cthroat felt 'unappreciated', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FShe allegedly told Mr Abukhait that
OL,8,FPexton had attempted to murder two of
OL,9,Fher boyfriends and hired two people to
OL,10,Fbeat up someone called David.
OL,12,FMs Abbott also asked her nephew if she
OL,13,Fshould apply for a restraining order
OL,14,Fand even wrote a note about it on a
OL,15,Fscrap of paper, jurors heard.
OL,17,FOn June 10, the defendant called her
OL,18,Fsister nine times, the final call
OL,19,Flasting just over 15 minutes.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
