PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776345056
OL,3,CWoman accused of slashing sister's
OL,4,Cthroat felt 'unappreciated', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FBill Boyce KC, prosecuting, said it
OL,8,Fwas "no coincidence" Ms Abbott was not
OL,9,Fseen or heard from after she took her
OL,10,Fcorgi dog, Prince, for a walk that
OL,11,Fmorning.
OL,13,FHe alleged Pexton was the last person
OL,14,Fto see her alive having fatally
OL,15,Fattacked her in her home and leaving
OL,16,Fjust before 2pm.
OL,18,FPexton was arrested on June 18 after
OL,19,Fthe discovery of her sister's watch in
OL,20,Fher bag.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
