PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776345056
OL,3,CWoman accused of slashing sister's
OL,4,Cthroat felt 'unappreciated', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FShe denied killing her sister and
OL,8,Fclaimed Ms Abbott had given her the
OL,9,FRolex to "keep for her", jurors heard.
OL,11,FPexton, of no fixed address, denies
OL,12,Fmurder and the Old Bailey trial
OL,13,Fcontinues.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
